Module mesakit.graph.core
Package com.telenav.mesakit.graph.collections

Class EdgeSet

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.mesakit.graph.collections.EdgeSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.string.Stringable, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.string.StringSource, Iterable<Edge>, Collection<Edge>, Set<Edge>
public class EdgeSet extends Object implements Set<Edge>, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.string.Stringable
A set of edges. Supports union(EdgeSet) and without(Set) operations, that logically combine this set of edges with another set of edges without creating a physical set.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
